  "detailed_description": "Welcome to a peaceful medieval village, where life is safe and calm. But one fateful night, everything changes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565680/extras/006dda6a8a6dd2b7535e4b0cefbd46ca.poster.avif?t=1725043610\" width=600 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565680/extras/006dda6a8a6dd2b7535e4b0cefbd46ca.webm?t=1725043610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565680/extras/006dda6a8a6dd2b7535e4b0cefbd46ca.mp4?t=1725043610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play as Jacob, an average medieval boy, on his quest to save the kingdom from a dark prophecy.<br><br>Jacob finds himself amid a whirlpool of magical events. Now the fate of his village (and whole kingdom) depends on him.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Help Jacob on his quest and save the kingdom from the dark prophecy,<br></li><li>Explore the environment and find solutions to move the plot forward,<br></li><li>Discover new items and fantastical locations,<br></li><li>Enjoy beautiful pixel-art locations.</li></ul><br>Featuring:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Choose your own adventure dialogues,<br></li><li>\"Look at/Use/Talk to\" interactions,<br></li><li>A dark prophecy and witchcraft.</li></ul><br>",
  "about_the_game": "Welcome to a peaceful medieval village, where life is safe and calm. But one fateful night, everything changes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565680/extras/006dda6a8a6dd2b7535e4b0cefbd46ca.poster.avif?t=1725043610\" width=600 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565680/extras/006dda6a8a6dd2b7535e4b0cefbd46ca.webm?t=1725043610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565680/extras/006dda6a8a6dd2b7535e4b0cefbd46ca.mp4?t=1725043610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play as Jacob, an average medieval boy, on his quest to save the kingdom from a dark prophecy.<br><br>Jacob finds himself amid a whirlpool of magical events. Now the fate of his village (and whole kingdom) depends on him.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Help Jacob on his quest and save the kingdom from the dark prophecy,<br></li><li>Explore the environment and find solutions to move the plot forward,<br></li><li>Discover new items and fantastical locations,<br></li><li>Enjoy beautiful pixel-art locations.</li></ul><br>Featuring:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Choose your own adventure dialogues,<br></li><li>\"Look at/Use/Talk to\" interactions,<br></li><li>A dark prophecy and witchcraft.</li></ul><br>",
